### Tes Register (Klik tombol panah hijau di sebelah kiri baris ini)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/register?username=dios&password=123

### Tes Login (Klik tombol panah hijau di sebelah kiri baris ini)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/login?username=dios&password=123

### ── REFRESH TOKEN & DENYLIST (Auth) ──

### Register (auth path used by the frontend)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "dios",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Login — returns accessToken (15 min, JWT) + refreshToken (7 days, opaque)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "dios",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Refresh — exchange refreshToken for a new (access, refresh) pair
### Copy the refreshToken from the /login response below:
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "PASTE_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE"
}

### Logout — revokes access token (jti -> denylist) and refresh token
### (hash -> revoked=1). Idempotent. Bearer header is optional.
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "refreshToken": "PASTE_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE"
}

### ── BRUTE-FORCE PROTECTION (LoginRateLimitService) ──
###
### After 5 FAILED login attempts from the same IP within a 15-minute
### window, the 6th attempt returns 429 Too Many Requests with a
### Retry-After header (in seconds). The bucket refills 5 tokens
### all at once after 15 minutes.
###
### To manually test: send 6 login requests with a wrong password.
###   - Requests 1-5 → 401 (each one also consumes a token)
###   - Request 6   → 429 + Retry-After header
###
### A successful login does NOT consume a token, so a legitimate
### user who occasionally mistypes their password is not affected.

### Wrong password #1 (401 + consumes 1 token)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "dios",
  "password": "WRONG_PASSWORD_1"
}

### Wrong password #2 (401 + consumes 1 token)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "dios",
  "password": "WRONG_PASSWORD_2"
}

### Wrong password #6 (429 + Retry-After header — bucket empty)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "dios",
  "password": "WRONG_PASSWORD_6"
}

### 1. Tambah Catatan Pengeluaran Baru
POST http://localhost:8080/api/bill/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "amount": 15000.00,
  "type": 0,
  "category": "Makanan",
  "description": "Mie Gacoan Cabang Manyar Sabrangan",
  "billDate": "2026-07-10"
}

### 2. Lihat Daftar Tagihan (Berdasarkan ID User)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/bill/list?userId=1

### 3. Hapus Tagihan (Ganti angka 1 dengan ID tagihan yang ingin dihapus)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/bill/delete?id=1

### Lihat Statistik Bulan Juli 2026
GET http://localhost:8080/api/bill/stats/monthly?userId=1&month=7&year=2026

### ── FITUR BUDGET ──

### Lihat ringkasan bulanan (dengan info budget)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/stats/summary?userId=1&month=7&year=2026

### Simpan / Update target anggaran bulanan
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/budget
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "monthlyBudget": 3000000
}

### Ambil anggaran tersimpan milik user
GET http://localhost:8080/api/budget/1

### ── DETAIL CHART INTERAKTIF ──

### Ambil daftar transaksi per kategori (untuk klik pie chart)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/stats/transactions?userId=1&category=Makanan&month=7&year=2026

### ── FITUR CUSTOM CATEGORIES ──

### Lihat semua custom category milik user
GET http://localhost:8080/api/categories?userId=1

### Tambah custom category baru (income)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "type": 1,
  "name": "Side Hustle"
}

### Tambah custom category baru (expense)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "type": 0,
  "name": "Coffee"
}

### Edit custom category (ganti 1 dengan ID category yang sebenarnya)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/categories/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "userId": 1,
  "type": 0,
  "name": "Coffee & Snacks"
}

### Hapus custom category
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/categories/1?userId=1

### Tambah transaksi dengan custom category baru (auto-create)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/bills
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "amount": 50.00,
  "type": 0,
  "category": "Pet Food",
  "description": "Cat food for Luna",
  "billDate": "2026-07-18"
}
